{"trainType":"科技英才班","grade":"2024","education":{"id":2,"nameZh":"本科"},"studentType":{"id":4,"nameZh":"普通"},"department":{"id":91,"code":"208","nameZh":"地球和空间科学学院"},"major":{"id":51,"code":"208*1","nameZh":"赵九章现代地球和空间科技英才班"},"majorDirection":null,"requiredCredits":167,"awardDegree":false,"beginSemester":"2024年秋季学期","directionGen":true,"moduleTree":[{"self":{"id":63892,"parent":48680,"type":"专业基础课程","typeEn":"Professional Basic Courses","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":0,"requiredCourseNum":0,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":0},"isLeaf":false,"children":[{"self":{"id":63894,"parent":63892,"type":"专业基础课程","typeEn":"Professional Basic Courses","major":"空间科学与技术","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":3,"requiredCourseNum":1,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[{"compulsory":true,"weeks":null,"totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":null,"course":{"id":140348,"code":"219002","nameZh":"数字信号处理B","nameEn":"Digital Signal Processing B","totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"credits":3,"introduction":"<p>本课程讲授数字信号处理基本理论和实现方法。内容上衔接信号与系统课程，并逐步过渡到为在数字设备上实现数字信号处理而需要的离散傅立叶变换（DFT）及其快速计算（FFT）；接下来是与系统分析有关的内容，包括离散时间系统的相位、结构与逆系统；最后是无限/有限冲激响应数字滤波器设计，这是与系统设计有关的内容。</p>","courseGradation":"专业基础","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["3秋"],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（闭卷）","department":{"id":614,"code":"219","nameZh":"集成电路学院（国家示范性微电子学院）"}}],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":0},"isLeaf":true},{"self":{"id":63893,"parent":63892,"type":"专业基础课程","typeEn":"Professional Basic Courses","major":"地球物理学","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":3,"requiredCourseNum":1,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[{"compulsory":true,"weeks":null,"totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":null,"course":{"id":140348,"code":"219002","nameZh":"数字信号处理B","nameEn":"Digital Signal Processing B","totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"credits":3,"introduction":"<p>本课程讲授数字信号处理基本理论和实现方法。内容上衔接信号与系统课程，并逐步过渡到为在数字设备上实现数字信号处理而需要的离散傅立叶变换（DFT）及其快速计算（FFT）；接下来是与系统分析有关的内容，包括离散时间系统的相位、结构与逆系统；最后是无限/有限冲激响应数字滤波器设计，这是与系统设计有关的内容。</p>","courseGradation":"专业基础","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["3秋"],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（闭卷）","department":{"id":614,"code":"219","nameZh":"集成电路学院（国家示范性微电子学院）"}}],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":1},"isLeaf":true}]},{"self":{"id":48681,"parent":48680,"type":"专业核心课程","typeEn":"Major Courses","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":5,"requiredCourseNum":3,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":20,"theoryPeriods":20,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":1,"course":{"id":14905,"code":"208702","nameZh":"地球系统科学讲座","nameEn":"Seminar in Earth System Science","totalPeriods":20,"theoryPeriods":20,"credits":1,"introduction":"<p>组织英才班学生3春赴中科院地质与地球物理研究所，由研究所组织高水平研究人员为英才班学生做地球系统科学方面的系列讲座，与学生研讨地球系统科学相关的前沿问题，并向学生介绍相关科学研究方法和科学仪器设备；学生选取其中的两个讲座撰写总结或前沿进展报告, 每个报告字数不少于1000字,或者只选取其中一个讲座撰写报告，字数不少于2500字（不包括参考文献）。</p>","courseGradation":"专业核心","seasons":"春"},"terms":["3春"],"remark":null,"examMode":"大作业（论文、报告、项目或作品等）","department":{"id":91,"code":"208","nameZh":"地球和空间科学学院"}},{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":40,"theoryPeriods":0,"praticePeriods":40,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":1,"course":{"id":8598,"code":"208703","nameZh":"野外与实践","nameEn":"Field andPractice","totalPeriods":40,"theoryPeriods":0,"credits":1,"introduction":"<p>要求英才班学生四年内至少参加该课程组织的野外／研究院所实习实践活动中的4次，每次实习结束后两周内要求提交不少于800字的实习总结报告，第四年秋季学期根据学生整体的实习表现、参与次数和实习报告质量给出最终成绩</p>","courseGradation":"专业核心","seasons":"秋"},"terms":["4秋"],"remark":null,"examMode":"大作业（论文、报告、项目或作品等）","department":{"id":91,"code":"208","nameZh":"地球和空间科学学院"}},{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"praticePeriods":null,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":3,"course":{"id":8597,"code":"208701","nameZh":"交叉研究实践","nameEn":"Interdisciplinary Research Practice","totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"credits":3,"introduction":"<p>本科阶段的科学研究是培养学生科研思维能力和科学兴趣的一个重要环节，对今后培养优秀的科研人才具有重要意义。本课程面向大三年级的地空学院英才班学生，通过老师授课、学生开展一年的科研实践、师生共同研讨等方式提高学生开展交叉科学研究的能力、科学论文撰写的能力以及进行学术报告和学术交流活动的能力。</p>","courseGradation":"专业核心","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["3秋"],"remark":null,"examMode":"大作业（论文、报告、项目或作品等）","department":{"id":91,"code":"208","nameZh":"地球和空间科学学院"}}],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":1},"isLeaf":true},{"self":{"id":48682,"parent":48680,"type":"专业选修课程","typeEn":"Major Selectives","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":"在导师指导下选修4个学分主修专业之外的其他专业（建议选择地空学院下设专业）的专业核心课","requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":4,"requiredCourseNum":0,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[{"compulsory":false,"weeks":null,"totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":20,"praticePeriods":40,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":null,"course":{"id":146151,"code":"ESS4702","nameZh":"地球系统野外综合实习","nameEn":"Integrated Field Study of Earth System Science","totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":20,"credits":2,"introduction":"<p>地球系统科学野外综合实习面向地空学院赵九章英才班大二学生。实习把课堂讲授和野外考察结合，以法国阿尔卑斯地区为例，让学生直观认识俯冲带大地构造现象，深入理解地球系统变化规律与机理。课程前期讲授岩石、矿物、构造等地质学背景知识，介绍法国阿尔卑斯地区的地质背景，为野外考察和研讨打基础。野外实习围绕板块构造、火山地震、冰川地貌、大气和空间观测开展教学，学生实地研讨地质现象、地形地貌形成机制，理解地球各圈层的相互作用。课程用英文讲授。</p>","courseGradation":"专业选修","seasons":"夏"},"terms":["2夏"],"remark":null,"examMode":"大作业（论文、报告、项目或作品等）","department":{"id":91,"code":"208","nameZh":"地球和空间科学学院"}}],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":2},"isLeaf":true}]}